summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the Library Board to acquire, by private purchase, Lot Nine (9), less the North Four (4) feet thereof; also Lots Ten (10), Eleven (11) and Twelve (12), all in Block Twenty-seven (27), Law's Second Addition to The City of Seattle, for a sum not to exceed Seven Thousand Two Hundred Dollars ($7,200), for library purposes, payment to be made from the Library Fund.
